A4.text: Haneda is the fifth busiest airport in the world by passenger traffic.

A5.text: In 2023, Haneda handled 17.9 million international passengers and 60.8 million domestic passengers, while Narita was used by 25.4 million international passengers and 7.7 million domestic passengers.
